---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import AnimatedImage from "../components/ui/animated-image";
---

<Layout title="关于我 - 思考随笔" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}>
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <main class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center md:items-start">
        <AnimatedImage
          client:load
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330"
          alt="个人头像"
          wrapperClassName="w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden gradient-bg flex-shrink-0"
          className="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-overlay opacity-80"
          animation="fade"
        />

        <div class="flex-1 fade-in">
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Jea</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
            前端工程师 | UI/UX设计师 | 技术写作者
          </p>

          <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-8">
            <p>
              你好！我是李明，一位热爱技术与设计的创作者。我在前端开发领域有着8年的经验，对用户体验设计充满热情。
            </p>
            <p>
              我相信技术应该服务于人，而不是相反。在我的职业生涯中，我始终致力于创造既美观又实用的数字产品，帮助用户解决实际问题。
            </p>
            <p>
              在这个博客中，我将分享我在技术、设计和生活方面的思考与实践经验。无论是前端开发的最佳实践，还是UI设计的美学原则，亦或是对数字生活的反思，我都希望能与你一同探讨。
            </p>
            <p>
              除了写代码和设计界面，我还喜欢摄影、阅读和旅行。这些爱好让我能够从不同角度观察世界，获取灵感。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8 slide-up">
            <a
              href="mailto:contact@example.com"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="bx bx-envelope mr-2 text-lg"></i>
              联系我
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://github.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="bx bxl-github mr-2 text-lg"></i>
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
            >
              <i class="bx bxl-twitter mr-2 text-lg"></i>
              Twitter
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 slide-up delay-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">技能与专长</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover-lift"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
              >
                <i class="bx bx-code-alt text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">前端开发</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              熟练掌握现代前端技术栈，包括HTML5、CSS3、JavaScript/TypeScript，以及React、Vue等框架。
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >React</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Vue</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >TypeScript</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Tailwind CSS</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Next.js</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover-lift"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400"
              >
                <i class="bx bx-palette text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">UI/UX 设计</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              擅长用户体验设计与界面设计，注重用户调研、交互设计和视觉美学的和谐统一。
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >Figma</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >用户研究</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >原型设计</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >交互设计</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >设计系统</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover-lift"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400"
              >
                <i class="bx bx-book-open text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">技术写作</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              热衷于分享技术知识和经验，擅长将复杂概念转化为清晰、易懂的文章和教程。
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >教程创作</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >技术博客</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >文档编写</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >演讲分享</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover-lift"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400"
              >
                <i class="bx bx-camera text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">摄影与创意</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              将摄影作为创意表达的媒介，擅长捕捉生活中的美好瞬间和独特视角。
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >街头摄影</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >风景摄影</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >人文纪实</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full"
                >后期处理</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 slide-up delay-300">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">联系我</h2>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
            如果你对我的文章有任何问题，或者想要探讨合作机会，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              >
                <i class="bx bx-envelope text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 block"
                  >邮箱</span
                >
                <a
                  href="mailto:contact@example.com"
                  class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors"
                  >contact@example.com</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              >
                <i class="bx bxl-twitter text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 block"
                  >Twitter</span
                >
                <a
                  href="https://twitter.com"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors"
                  >@limingtw</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              >
                <i class="bx bxl-github text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 block"
                  >GitHub</span
                >
                <a
                  href="https://github.com"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors"
                  >github.com/liming</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
              >
                <i class="bx bxl-linkedin text-xl"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 block"
                  >LinkedIn</span
                >
                <a
                  href="https://linkedin.com"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors"
                  >linkedin.com/in/liming</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
